videos.headline: Iowa scores first touchdown of the game
videos.description: Nathan Stanley rolls out to his right and throws a touchdown to TE Noah Fant as Iowa takes the lead over Wyoming 7-3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Iowa scores first touchdown of the game) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wyoming's Zaleski whiffs on punt attempt
videos.description: Wyoming freshman punter Tim Zaleski lets go of the ball too early and completely misses on his punt attempt, and Iowa is quick to jump on the loose ball.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Wyoming's Zaleski whiffs on punt attempt) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanley throws 45-yard TD to pad Iowa's lead
videos.description: Iowa extends its lead with a 45-yard play-action pass to WR Nick Easley, giving the Hawkeyes a 21-3 lead over Wyoming.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Stanley throws 45-yard TD to pad Iowa's lead) 2017/09/02 ESHEET
